description:
A special delivery from the city has arrived, with a new look for every season! Customise your character with the following four outfits:

- Spring Cow-digan: Look udderly adorable!
- Summer Raincoat: Be shower-chic in any storm!
- Autumn Aviator Jacket: You can't feel blue in this autumn hue! 
- Winter Peacoat: Makes even the chilliest winds more ap-pea-ling!


*These items will appear in your dresser once you have accepted it from the blue Deposit Box in front of your house.
*Headwear can be equipped by selecting it as a hairstyle.
*Outfits can be changed by using the mirror or dresser in your house.
name: Seasonal Outfits Set
